items.title: Musk gets his Texas wish. SpaceX launch site approved as new city of Starbase
items.description: A vote was held Saturday to formally organize Starbase as a city.

items.title: WATCH:  Boy has encounter with 'friendly' dolphin
items.description: A boy and his father had the encounter of a lifetime while fishing off the coast of Perth, Australia, when a dolphin swam up to their boat.
